-monitor-2026-03-01.jpg\" alt=\"Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><figcaption>来源：<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"trend-item-copy\"><p class=\"trend-month-kicker\">2026.03 · Hotspot 01</p><h3>Google Stitch 推动 Vibe Design</h3><p><strong>发生了什么：</strong>3 月关于 Stitch 的报道把“vibe designing”推到台前：用户用业务目标、情绪、参考和自然语言生成 UI 与前端代码。</p><p><strong>设计启发：</strong>设计师要学会把抽象感受翻译成布局、密度、色彩、字体和交互规则。</p></div></section><section class=\"trend-item\" id=\"trend-2\"><figure class=\"trend-figure\"><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"./assets/article-images/trend-source-images/ai-trend-monitor-2026-03-01.jpg\" alt=\"Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><figcaption>来源：<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"trend-item-copy\"><p class=\"trend-month-kicker\">2026.03 · Hotspot 02</p><h3>语音输入进入 UI 设计工具</h3><p><strong>发生了什么：</strong>Stitch 更新加入语音输入，用户可以通过口述请求设计修改、变体和反馈。</p><p><strong>设计启发：</strong>语音适合评审和快速探索，但关键决策仍要沉淀为文字规范。</p></div></section><section class=\"trend-item\" id=\"trend-3\"><figure class=\"trend-figure\"><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"./assets/article-images/trend-source-images/ai-trend-monitor-2026-03-01.jpg\" alt=\"Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><figcaption>来源：<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"trend-item-copy\"><p class=\"trend-month-kicker\">2026.03 · Hotspot 03</p><h3>无限画布支持发散探索</h3><p><strong>发生了什么：</strong>Stitch 的无限画布让多个方向、多个版本和多个流程可以同时展开。</p><p><strong>设计启发：</strong>早期设计可以先发散 5-10 个方向，再用目标和约束筛选。</p></div></section><section class=\"trend-item\" id=\"trend-4\"><figure class=\"trend-figure\"><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"./assets/article-images/trend-source-images/ai-trend-monitor-2026-03-01.jpg\" alt=\"Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><figcaption>来源：<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"trend-item-copy\"><p class=\"trend-month-kicker\">2026.03 · Hotspot 04</p><h3>设计 Agent 追踪项目历史</h3><p><strong>发生了什么：</strong>新版 Stitch 的设计 Agent 会跟踪项目历史，提高连续修改和上下文理解能力。</p><p><strong>设计启发：</strong>文件命名、版本记录和决策说明会直接影响 AI 协作质量。</p></div></section><section class=\"trend-item\" id=\"trend-5\"><figure class=\"trend-figure\"><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"./assets/article-images/trend-source-images/ai-trend-monitor-2026-03-01.jpg\" alt=\"Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><figcaption>来源：<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"trend-item-copy\"><p class=\"trend-month-kicker\">2026.03 · Hotspot 05</p><h3>DESIGN.md 成为设计系统载体</h3><p><strong>发生了什么：</strong>Stitch 更新提到 DESIGN.md，用于在不同项目中携带设计系统信息。</p><p><strong>设计启发：</strong>把品牌、组件、页面模式、禁忌项和验收标准写成 AI 可读文档。</p></div></section><section class=\"trend-item\" id=\"trend-6\"><figure class=\"trend-figure\"><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"./assets/article-images/trend-source-images/ai-trend-monitor-2026-03-01.jpg\" alt=\"Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><figcaption>来源：<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"trend-item-copy\"><p class=\"trend-month-kicker\">2026.03 · Hotspot 06</p><h3>市场开始重新评估设计工具护城河</h3><p><strong>发生了什么：</strong>Stitch 报道同时提到 Figma 等设计工具的市场压力，说明 AI 生成 UI 已被视为工具格局变量。</p><p><strong>设计启发：</strong>判断工具价值要看协作网络、资产沉淀、系统规范和生态，而不是只看生成速度。</p></div></section><section class=\"trend-item\" id=\"trend-7\"><figure class=\"trend-figure\"><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"./assets/article-images/trend-source-images/ai-trend-monitor-2026-03-01.jpg\" alt=\"Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><figcaption>来源：<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/figma-stock-sinks-google-vibe-design-stitch-ai-tool-2026-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Business Insider: Google Stitch / vibe design</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"trend-item-copy\"><p class=\"trend-month-kicker\">2026.03 · Hotspot 07</p><h3>Vibe Design 不是放弃专业</h3><p><strong>发生了什么：</strong>Vibe Design 的价值在于快速把方向变成可见方案，但最终仍依赖设计判断来筛选、约束和修正。</p><p><strong>设计启发：</strong>设计师要强化“方向判断”和“质量验收”，避免只追求生成数量。</p></div></section><section class=\"trend-item\" id=\"trend-8\"><figure class=\"trend-figure\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.17296\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"./assets/article-images/trend-source-images/ar5iv-real-11.png\" alt=\"GUIDE: GenAI Units In Digital Design Education\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><figcaption>来源：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.17296\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GUIDE: GenAI Units In Digital Design Education</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"trend-item-copy\"><p class=\"trend-month-kicker\">2026.03 · Hotspot 08</p><h3>AI 设计教育开始体系化</h3><p><strong>发生了什么：</strong>GUIDE 论文展示了以标准化单元、可运行实验和课程实例组织生成式 AI 教育的方式。</p><p><strong>设计启发：</strong>AI 设计能力培养也需要课程化：概念、案例、实验、作业和评估标准。</p></div></section><section class=\"trend-item\" id=\"trend-9\"><figure class=\"trend-figure\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.17296\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"./assets/article-images/trend-source-images/ar5iv-real-11.png\" alt=\"GUIDE: GenAI Units In Digital Design Education\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><figcaption>来源：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.17296\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GUIDE: GenAI Units In Digital Design Education</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"trend-item-copy\"><p class=\"trend-month-kicker\">2026.03 · Hotspot 09</p><h3>可运行实验比概念学习更有效</h3><p><strong>发生了什么：</strong>GUIDE 的方式强调 runnable labs，这对设计学习同样适用。</p><p><strong>设计启发：</strong>训练 AI 设计能力时，不只看文章，要用真实任务反复练习。</p></div></section><section class=\"trend-item\" id=\"trend-10\"><figure class=\"trend-figure\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.17296\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"./assets/article-images/trend-source-images/ar5iv-real-11.png\" alt=\"GUIDE: GenAI Units In Digital Design Education\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><figcaption>来源：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.17296\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GUIDE: GenAI Units In Digital Design Education</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"trend-item-copy\"><p class=\"trend-month-kicker\">2026.03 